Class LifetimeTotals

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team06.LifetimeTotals
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LifetimeTotals
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    LifetimeTotals class that takes information from the api and saves it under the totals tab so the user can see their totals. Info is pulled from the FitBit.api so totals are persistent.
